  "title": "F&B Service Crew [Islandwide | 5/6 days | Gross salary up to $3000+] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>F&B Service Crew</strong></h3><p><strong>Basic Salary: $2150 + OT </strong></p><ul><li><strong>5 Days - Gross Salary $2400 - $2600</strong></li><li><strong>6 Days - Gross Salary $3000++</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Working Days & Hours: 5 / 6 Days (44hrs - Can Choose)</strong><br /><strong>Working Location: Islandwide</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Greeting customers and answering questions about the menu.</li><li>Taking food and beverage orders and processing payments.</li><li>Serving food and beverages to customers.</li><li>Preparing food items, which may include cooking, assembling, and garnishing.</li><li>Cleaning tables, floors, and other areas of the establishment.</li><li>Maintaining the overall cleanliness and organization of the dining and working areas.</li><li>Washing dishes and cutlery</li><li>Operating cash registers and handling transactions.</li><li>Stocking supplies and refilling items like condiments and napkins.</li><li>Assisting with opening or closing duties, as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Training Provided</li><li>Will require to take turn wash dishes</li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
